"                     ▲            ▲\n"
"                     │            │\n"
"   ┌────────────┬────┴────────────┴─────┬────────────┐\n"
"   │            │                       │            │\n"
"   ▼            ▼                       ▼            ▼\n"
"┌────┐       ┌────┐                  ┌────┐       ┌────┐\n"
"│ S3 │◀─────▶│ S4 │                  │ S5 │◀─────▶│ S6 │\n"
"└────┘       └────┘                  └────┘       └────┘\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"  <?dbfo keep-together=\"always\"?>\n"
"                  ┌────┐       ┌────┐\n"
"                  │ S1 │◀─────▶│ S2 │\n"
"                  └────┘       └────┘\n"
"                     ▲            ▲\n"
"                     │            │\n"
"   ┌────────────┬────┴────────────┴─────┬────────────┐\n"
"   │            │                       │            │\n"
"   ▼            ▼                       ▼            ▼\n"
"┌────┐       ┌────┐                  ┌────┐       ┌────┐\n"
"│ S3 │◀─────▶│ S4 │                  │ S5 │◀─────▶│ S6 │\n"
"└────┘       └────┘                  └────┘       └────┘\n"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In <xref linkend=\"ex-ldap-replication-six-replicas\"/> , each pair is in a "
"separate location. S1 and S2 are the suppliers, and S3, S4, S5, and S6 are "
"consumers of S1 and S2. Each pair of servers replicate to each other. S3, "
"S4, S5 and S6 can accept writes, though most of the replication is done "
"through S1 and S2. This setup provides geographic separation for high "
"availability and scaling."
msgstr ""
"<xref linkend=\"ex-ldap-replication-six-replicas\"/> は各サーバ対を別々の場所"
"に配置した場合の構成例です。 S1 と S2 はサプライヤ、 S3, S4, S5, S6 は S1 と "
"S2 のコンシューマとして構成します。また、各サーバ対はお互いにレプリケーション"
"しているものとし、 S3, S4, S5, S6 でも書き込み要求は受け付けるものとします"
"が、ほとんどのレプリケーションは S1, S2 で行われます、このような構成は、高可"
"用性と分散処理の両方を、地理的な離れた場所から提供する際の例となります。"

#. Tag: title
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:240
#, no-c-format
msgid "Six replicas with read-only consumers"
msgstr "読み込み専用コンシューマのある 6 つのレプリカ"

#. Tag: screen
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:241
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"             ┌────┐       ┌────┐\n"
"             │ S1 │◀─────▶│ S2 │\n"
"             └────┘       └────┘\n"
"                │            │\n"
"                │            │\n"
"   ┌────────────┼────────────┼────────────┐\n"
"   │            │            │            │\n"
"   ▼            ▼            ▼            ▼\n"
"┌────┐       ┌────┐       ┌────┐       ┌────┐\n"
"│ S3 │       │ S4 │       │ S5 │       │ S6 │\n"
"└────┘       └────┘       └────┘       └────┘\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"             ┌────┐       ┌────┐\n"
"             │ S1 │◀─────▶│ S2 │\n"
"             └────┘       └────┘\n"
"                │            │\n"
"                │            │\n"
"   ┌────────────┼────────────┼────────────┐\n"
"   │            │            │            │\n"
"   ▼            ▼            ▼            ▼\n"
"┌────┐       ┌────┐       ┌────┐       ┌────┐\n"
"│ S3 │       │ S4 │       │ S5 │       │ S6 │\n"
"└────┘       └────┘       └────┘       └────┘\n"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In <xref linkend=\"ex-ldap-replication-six-replicas-read-only\"/> , S1 and "
"S2 are the suppliers, and the other four servers are read-only consumers. "
"All changes occur on S1 and S2, and are propagated to the four replicas. "
"Read-only consumers can be configured to store only a subset of the "
"database, or partial entries, to limit data exposure. You could have a "
"fractional read-only server in a DMZ, for example, so that if data is "
"exposed, changes can not propagate back to the other replicas."
msgstr ""
"<xref linkend=\"ex-ldap-replication-six-replicas-read-only\"/> では、 S1 と "
"S2 の両方がサプライヤとなり、残りの 4 つのサーバは読み込み専用のコンシューマ"
"として構成する場合の例となります。全ての書き込み要求は S1, S2 でのみ行われ、"
"残りの 4 つのサーバに複製していく構成です。読み込み専用のコンシューマには、"
"データ開示を最小限に留めるため、データベースの一部や項目の一部のみを保存させ"
"るようにすることもできます。このように部分的な複製のみを持つ構成は DMZ のよう"
"なネットワークを持つ場合に最適で、この場合は DMZ 内に配置したコンシューマへの"
"書き込みはできなくなります。"

#. Tag: title
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:268
#, no-c-format
msgid "Terminology"
msgstr "用語"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the example topologies we have seen that &ds389a; can take on a number of "
"roles in a topology. The following list clarifies the terminology."
msgstr ""
"ここまでに説明してきた &ds389a; の構成例やこの後の説明では、様々な用語を使用"
"しています。下記ではそれら用語に対する説明を示しています。"

#. Tag: term
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:275
#, no-c-format
msgid "Replica"
msgstr "レプリカ"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:277
#, no-c-format
msgid "An instance of &ds389a; with an attached database."
msgstr "データベースを持つ &ds389a; のインスタンスを意味しています。"

#. Tag: term
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:283
#, no-c-format
msgid "Read-write replica"
msgstr "読み書き可能なレプリカ"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:285
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A replica with a full copy of a database, that accepts read and write "
"operations."
msgstr ""
"読み込みと書き込みの両方の要求を受け付けることができる、データベースの完全コ"
"ピーを持つレプリカを意味しています。"

#. Tag: term
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "Read-only replica"
msgstr "読み込み専用レプリカ"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A replica with a full copy of a database, that only accepts read operations."
msgstr ""
"読み込み要求のみを受け付けることができる、データベースの完全コピーを持つレプ"
"リカを意味しています。"

#. Tag: term
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:301
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fractional read-only replica"
msgstr "部分的な複製のみを持つレプリカ"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:303
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A replica with a partial copy of a database, that only accepts read- only "
"operations."
msgstr ""
"データベースのうちの一部のみを複製し、読み込み要求のみを受け付けることができ"
"るレプリカを意味しています。"

#. Tag: term
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:310
#, no-c-format
msgid "Supplier"
msgstr "サプライヤ"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:312
#, no-c-format
msgid "A replica that supplies data from its database to another replica."
msgstr ""
"他のレプリカにデータベースの内容を提供することができるレプリカを意味していま"
"す。"

#. Tag: term
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:318
#, no-c-format
msgid "Consumer"
msgstr "コンシューマ"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:320
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A replica that receives data from another replica to write into its database."
msgstr ""
"他のレプリカからデータを受け取って、自身のデータベースに書き込むレプリカを意"
"味しています。"

#. Tag: term
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:327
#, no-c-format
msgid "Replication agreement"
msgstr "レプリケーション同意"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The configuration of a server defining its supplier and consumer relation to "
"another replica."
msgstr ""
"他のレプリカとの関係性 (サプライヤ／コンシューマ) に対するサーバ設定を意味し"
"ています。"

#. Tag: term
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:336
#, no-c-format
msgid "Topology"
msgstr "構成"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:338
#, no-c-format
msgid "A set of replicas connected via replication agreements."
msgstr "レプリケーション同意を介したレプリカ同士の接続構成を意味しています。"

#. Tag: term
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:344
#, no-c-format
msgid "Replica ID"
msgstr "レプリカ ID"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:346
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A unique identifier of the &ds389; instance within the replication topology."
msgstr ""
"レプリケーション構成内で重複しない &ds389; のインスタンス識別子を意味していま"
"す。"

#. Tag: term
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:353
#, no-c-format
msgid "Replication manager"
msgstr "レプリケーションマネージャ"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:355
#, no-c-format
msgid "An account with replication rights in the directory."
msgstr "ディレクトリ内でレプリケーション権限を持つアカウントを意味しています。"

#. Tag: title
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:364
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring replication"
msgstr "レプリケーションの設定"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:365
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first example sets up a two node bi-directional replication with a "
"single read-only server, as a minimal starting example. In the following "
"examples, the host names of the two read-write nodes are RW1 and RW2, and "
"the read-only server is RO1. (Use your own host names.)"
msgstr ""
"最小構成例として、まずは 2 ノードの双方向レプリケーションと 1 ノードの読み込"
"み専用サーバを構成してみます。下記の例では、読み書き可能なレプリカのサーバ名"
"は RW1, RW2 とし、読み込み専用のレプリカのサーバ名は RO1 とします (もちろん必"
"要に応じて自由な名前を設定してかまいません) 。"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:371
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All servers should have a back-end with an identical suffix. Only one "
"server, RW1, needs an initial copy of the database."
msgstr ""
"この構成内にあるサーバには、全て同じサフィックスを設定する必要があります。ま"
"た、初期状態では RW1 にのみデータが存在するものとします。"

#. Tag: title
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:377
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring two-node replication"
msgstr "2 ノードレプリケーションの設定"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:378
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following commands configure the read-write replicas in a two-node setup "
"( <xref linkend=\"ex-ldap-replication-two-replicas\"/> ), with the host "
"names RW1 and RW2. (Use your own host names.)"
msgstr ""
"下記のコマンドは 2 ノード構成 ( <xref linkend=\"ex-ldap-replication-two-"
"replicas\"/> ) の場合のコマンド例で、ホスト名を RW1, RW2 にしています (実際に"
"は独自の名前でかまいません) 。"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:399
#, no-c-format
msgid "First, configure RW1:"
msgstr "まずは RW1 側を設定します:"

#. Tag: screen
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:403
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>INSTANCE-NAME</replaceable> "
"replication create-manager</command>\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>INSTANCE-NAME</replaceable> "
"replication enable</command> \\\n"
"<command>--suffix <replaceable>dc=example,dc=com</replaceable></command> \\\n"
"<command>--role supplier --replica-id <replaceable>1</replaceable> --bind-dn "
"\"cn=replication manager,cn=config\"</command>\n"
msgstr ""
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>インスタンス名</replaceable> "
"replication create-manager</command>\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>インスタンス名</replaceable> "
"replication enable</command> \\\n"
"<command>--suffix <replaceable>dc=example,dc=com</replaceable></command> \\\n"
"<command>--role supplier --replica-id <replaceable>1</replaceable> --bind-dn "
"\"cn=replication manager,cn=config\"</command>\n"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:408
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure RW2:"
msgstr "RW2 側の設定は下記のようになります:"

#. Tag: screen
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:411
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>INSTANCE-NAME</replaceable> "
"replication create-manager</command>\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>INSTANCE-NAME</replaceable> "
"replication enable</command> \\\n"
"<command>--suffix <replaceable>dc=example,dc=com</replaceable></command> \\\n"
"<command>--role supplier --replica-id <replaceable>2</replaceable> --bind-dn "
"\"cn=replication manager,cn=config\"</command>\n"
msgstr ""
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>インスタンス名</replaceable> "
"replication create-manager</command>\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>インスタンス名</replaceable> "
"replication enable</command> \\\n"
"<command>--suffix <replaceable>dc=example,dc=com</replaceable></command> \\\n"
"<command>--role supplier --replica-id <replaceable>2</replaceable> --bind-dn "
"\"cn=replication manager,cn=config\"</command>\n"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:416
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will create the replication metadata required on RW1 and RW2. Note the "
"difference in the <option>replica-id</option> between the two servers. This "
"also creates the replication manager account, which is an account with "
"replication rights for authenticating between the two nodes."
msgstr ""
"上記のコマンドを実行することで、 RW1, RW2 の両方にレプリケーション用のデータ"
"を設定することができます。なお、 RW1 と RW2 では <option>replica-id</option> "
"の値が異なっていることに注意してください。また、このコマンドを実行すると、レ"
"プリケーションマネージャのアカウントを作成することになります。このアカウント"
"は、 2 つのノードが互いに認証する際に使用するアカウントとなります。"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:422
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"RW1 and RW2 are now both configured to have replication metadata. The next "
"step is to create the first agreement for outbound data from RW1 to RW2."
msgstr ""
"これで RW1 と RW2 の間でレプリケーションを行う準備ができました。あとは RW1 か"
"ら RW2 に対して、データを発信するための最初の合意を作成します。"

#. Tag: screen
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:426
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<?dbfo keep-together=\"always\"?>\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>INSTANCE-NAME</replaceable> repl-"
"agmt create</command> \\\n"
"<command>--suffix <replaceable>dc=example,dc=com</replaceable></command> \\\n"
"<command>--host=<replaceable>RW2</replaceable> --port=636 --conn-protocol "
"LDAPS --bind-dn \"cn=replication manager,cn=config\"</command> \\\n"
"<command>--bind-passwd <replaceable>PASSWORD</replaceable> --bind-method "
"SIMPLE <replaceable>RW1_to_RW2</replaceable></command>\n"
msgstr ""
"<?dbfo keep-together=\"always\"?>\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>インスタンス名</replaceable> repl-"
"agmt create</command> \\\n"
"<command>--suffix <replaceable>dc=example,dc=com</replaceable></command> \\\n"
"<command>--host=<replaceable>RW2</replaceable> --port=636 --conn-protocol "
"LDAPS --bind-dn \"cn=replication manager,cn=config\"</command> \\\n"
"<command>--bind-passwd <replaceable>パスワード</replaceable> --bind-method "
"SIMPLE <replaceable>RW1_to_RW2</replaceable></command>\n"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:432
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Data does not flow from RW1 to RW2 until after a full synchronization of the "
"database, which is called an initialization or reinit. This resets all "
"database content on RW2 to match the content of RW1. Run the following "
"command to trigger a reinit of the data:"
msgstr ""
"上記のコマンドだけではデータベースの同期が始まりません。同期を始めるには、初"
"期化または再初期化と呼ばれる完全同期が必要となります。初期化または再初期化を"
"行うと、 RW2 側の全てのデータがリセットされ、 RW1 と全く同じデータになりま"
"す。これを行うには、下記のように入力して実行します:"

#. Tag: screen
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:438
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>INSTANCE-NAME</replaceable> repl-"
"agmt init</command> \\\n"
"<command>--suffix <replaceable>dc=example,dc=com</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>RW1_to_RW2</replaceable></command>\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>インスタンス名</replaceable> repl-"
"agmt init</command> \\\n"
"<command>--suffix <replaceable>dc=example,dc=com</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>RW1_to_RW2</replaceable></command>\n"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:442
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check the status by running this command on RW1:"
msgstr "あとは RW1 側で下記のようなコマンドを入力して実行し、状況を確認します:"

#. Tag: screen
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:445
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>INSTANCE-NAME</replaceable> repl-"
"agmt init-status</command> \\\n"
"<command>--suffix <replaceable>dc=example,dc=com</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>RW1_to_RW2</replaceable></command>\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>インスタンス名</replaceable> repl-"
"agmt init-status</command> \\\n"
"<command>--suffix <replaceable>dc=example,dc=com</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>RW1_to_RW2</replaceable></command>\n"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:449
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When it is finished, you should see an <literal>Agreement successfully "
"initialized</literal> message. If you get an error message, check the errors "
"log. Otherwise, you should see the identical content from RW1 on RW2."
msgstr ""
"同期が完了すると、 <literal>Agreement successfully initialized</literal> とい"
"うメッセージが表示されるはずです。それ以外のエラーメッセージが表示された場合"
"は、エラーログを調べてみてください。エラーが表示されなければ、 RW1 と RW2 は"
"全く同じデータになっているはずです。"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:454
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Finally, to make this bi-directional, configure a replication agreement from "
"RW2 outbound to RW1:"
msgstr ""
"あとはデータを双方向に複製するため、 RW2 から RW1 に対するレプリケーション合"
"意も設定します:"

#. Tag: screen
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:458
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>INSTANCE-NAME</replaceable> repl-"
"agmt create</command> \\\n"
"<command>--suffix <replaceable>dc=example,dc=com</replaceable></command> \\\n"
"<command>--host=<replaceable>RW1</replaceable> --port=636 --conn-protocol "
"LDAPS</command> \\\n"
"<command>--bind-dn \"cn=replication manager,cn=config\" --bind-passwd "
"<replaceable>PASSWORD</replaceable></command> \\\n"
"<command>--bind-method SIMPLE <replaceable>RW2_to_RW1</replaceable></"
"command>\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>インスタンス名</replaceable> repl-"
"agmt create</command> \\\n"
"<command>--suffix <replaceable>dc=example,dc=com</replaceable></command> \\\n"
"<command>--host=<replaceable>RW1</replaceable> --port=636 --conn-protocol "
"LDAPS</command> \\\n"
"<command>--bind-dn \"cn=replication manager,cn=config\" --bind-passwd "
"<replaceable>パスワード</replaceable></command> \\\n"
"<command>--bind-method SIMPLE <replaceable>RW2_to_RW1</replaceable></"
"command>\n"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Changes made on either RW1 or RW2 are now replicated to the other. Check "
"replication status on either server with the following command:"
msgstr ""
"これで RW1 と RW2 の双方向レプリケーションが完成し、一方での変更が他方にも反"
"映されるようになっています。いずれかのサーバで下記のようなコマンドを入力して"
"実行し、状態を確認してください:"

#. Tag: screen
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:469
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>INSTANCE-NAME</replaceable> repl-"
"agmt status</command> \\\n"
"<command>--suffix <replaceable>dc=example,dc=com</replaceable></command> \\\n"
"<command>--bind-dn \"cn=replication manager,cn=config\"</command> \\\n"
"<command>--bind-passwd <replaceable>PASSWORD</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>RW2_to_RW1</replaceable></command>\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>インスタンス名</replaceable> repl-"
"agmt status</command> \\\n"
"<command>--suffix <replaceable>dc=example,dc=com</replaceable></command> \\\n"
"<command>--bind-dn \"cn=replication manager,cn=config\"</command> \\\n"
"<command>--bind-passwd <replaceable>パスワード</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>RW2_to_RW1</replaceable></command>\n"

#. Tag: title
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:478
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring a read-only node"
msgstr "読み込み専用ノードの設定"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:479
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a read-only node, start by creating the replication manager "
"account and metadata. The hostname of the example server is RO3:"
msgstr ""
"読み込み専用ノードを作成するには、まずレプリケーションマネージャのアカウント"
"とメタデータを作成するところから始めます。ここでのサーバ名は RO3 とします:"

#. Tag: title
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:486
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a strong replication manager password"
msgstr "強力なレプリケーションマネージャパスワードの作成について"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:487
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The replication manager should be considered equivalent to the directory "
"manager in terms of security and access, and should have a strong password."
msgstr ""
"レプリケーションマネージャのアカウントはディレクトリマネージャのアカウントと"
"同等の権限を持つことから、セキュリティを確保するために強力なパスワードを設定"
"しておくことを強くお勧めします。"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:492
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you create different replication manager passwords for each server, be "
"sure to keep track of which password belongs to which server. For example, "
"when you configure the outbound connection in RW1's replication agreement, "
"you need to set the replication manager password to the RW2 replication "
"manager password."
msgstr ""
"各サーバで異なるレプリケーションマネージャのパスワードを設定する場合は、それ"
"ぞれのサーバが使用するアカウントをよく覚えておいてください。たとえば RW1 側の"
"レプリケーション同意を設定する場合、パスワードとして設定すべきなのは RW2 側の"
"レプリケーションマネージャのパスワードとなります。"

#. Tag: screen
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:500
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>INSTANCE_NAME</replaceable> "
"replication create-manager</command>\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command> dsconf <replaceable>INSTANCE_NAME</replaceable></"
"command> \\\n"
"<command>replication enable --suffix <replaceable>dc=EXAMPLE,dc=COM</"
"replaceable></command> \\\n"
"<command>--role consumer --bind-dn \"cn=replication manager,cn=config\"</"
"command>"
msgstr ""
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>インスタンス名</replaceable> "
"replication create-manager</command>\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command> dsconf <replaceable>インスタンス名</replaceable></"
"command> \\\n"
"<command>replication enable --suffix <replaceable>dc=EXAMPLE,dc=COM</"
"replaceable></command> \\\n"
"<command>--role consumer --bind-dn \"cn=replication manager,cn=config\"</"
"command>"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:505
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For a read-only replica, you do not provide a replica-id, and the role is "
"set to <literal>consumer</literal> . This allocates a special read-only "
"replica-id for all read-only replicas. After the read-only replica is "
"created, add the replication agreements from RW1 and RW2 to the read-only "
"instance. The following example is on RW1:"
msgstr ""
"なお、読み込み専用のレプリカに対しては、レプリカ ID の指定は不要であるほか、"
"役割の指定を <literal>consumer</literal> にします。これにより、特殊な読み込み"
"専用のレプリカ ID が割り当てられます。読み込み専用のレプリカを作成したら、あ"
"とは RW1, RW2 のそれぞれに対してレプリケーション同意を追加します。下記は RW1 "
"側での実行例です:"

#. Tag: screen
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:512
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>INSTANCE_NAME</replaceable></"
"command> \\\n"
"<command>repl-agmt create --suffix <replaceable>dc=EXAMPLE,dc=COM</"
"replaceable></command> \\\n"
"<command>--host=<replaceable>RO3</replaceable> --port=636 --conn-protocol "
"LDAPS</command> \\\n"
"<command>--bind-dn \"cn=replication manager,cn=config\" --bind-passwd "
"<replaceable>PASSWORD</replaceable></command>\n"
"<command>--bind-method SIMPLE <replaceable>RW1_to_RO3</replaceable></command>"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>インスタンス名</replaceable></"
"command> \\\n"
"<command>repl-agmt create --suffix <replaceable>dc=EXAMPLE,dc=COM</"
"replaceable></command> \\\n"
"<command>--host=<replaceable>RO3</replaceable> --port=636 --conn-protocol "
"LDAPS</command> \\\n"
"<command>--bind-dn \"cn=replication manager,cn=config\" --bind-passwd "
"<replaceable>パスワード</replaceable></command>\n"
"<command>--bind-method SIMPLE <replaceable>RW1_to_RO3</replaceable></command>"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:518
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following example, on RW2, configures the replication agreement between "
"RW2 and RO3:"
msgstr ""
"下記の例は、 RW2 と RO3 との間でのレプリケーション同意を RW2 側で設定する場合"
"の例です:"

#. Tag: screen
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:522
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>INSTANCE_NAME</replaceable> repl-"
"agmt create</command> \\\n"
"<command>--suffix <replaceable>dc=EXAMPLE,dc=COM</replaceable></command> \\\n"
"<command>--host=<replaceable>RO3</replaceable> --port=636 --conn-protocol "
"LDAPS</command> \\\n"
"<command>--bind-dn \"cn=replication manager,cn=config\" --bind-passwd "
"<replaceable>PASSWORD</replaceable></command> \\\n"
"<command>--bind-method SIMPLE <replaceable>RW2_to_RO3</replaceable></"
"command>\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>インスタンス名</replaceable> repl-"
"agmt create</command> \\\n"
"<command>--suffix <replaceable>dc=EXAMPLE,dc=COM</replaceable></command> \\\n"
"<command>--host=<replaceable>RO3</replaceable> --port=636 --conn-protocol "
"LDAPS</command> \\\n"
"<command>--bind-dn \"cn=replication manager,cn=config\" --bind-passwd "
"<replaceable>パスワード</replaceable></command> \\\n"
"<command>--bind-method SIMPLE <replaceable>RW2_to_RO3</replaceable></"
"command>\n"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:529
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After these steps are completed, you can use either RW1 or RW2 to perform "
"the initialization of the database on RO3. The following example initializes "
"RO3 from RW2:"
msgstr ""
"これらの作業が完了したら、あとは RW1, RW2 から RO3 へデータベースの初期化を行"
"います。下記の例では、 RW2 から RO3 に初期化を行っています:"

#. Tag: screen
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:534
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>INSTANCE_NAME</replaceable> repl-"
"agmt init</command>\n"
"<command>--suffix dc=<replaceable>EXAMPLE,dc=COM</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>RW2_to_RO3</replaceable></command>\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>インスタンス名</replaceable> repl-"
"agmt init</command>\n"
"<command>--suffix dc=<replaceable>EXAMPLE,dc=COM</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>RW2_to_RO3</replaceable></command>\n"

#. Tag: title
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:542
#, no-c-format
msgid "Monitoring and healthcheck"
msgstr "監視とヘルスチェック"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:543
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <command>dsconf</command> command includes a monitoring option. You can "
"check the status of each replica status directly on the replicas, or from "
"other hosts. The following example commands are run on RW1, checking the "
"status on two remote replicas, and then on itself:"
msgstr ""
"<command>dsconf</command> コマンドには監視オプションが用意されています。この"
"コマンドを実行することで、レプリカ内で直接状態を確認することができるほか、他"
"のホストからでも実行することができます。下記の例は RW1 内での実行例で、 2 つ"
"のレプリカに対する状態の確認と、自分自身の確認をそれぞれ行っています:"

#. Tag: screen
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:548
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<?dbfo keep-together=\"always\"?>\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf -D \"cn=Directory Manager\" ldap://"
"<replaceable>RW2</replaceable> replication monitor</command>\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf -D \"cn=Directory Manager\" ldap://"
"<replaceable>RO3</replaceable> replication monitor</command>\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf -D \"cn=Directory Manager\" ldap://"
"<replaceable>RW1</replaceable> replication monitor</command>\n"
msgstr ""
"<?dbfo keep-together=\"always\"?>\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf -D \"cn=Directory Manager\" ldap://"
"<replaceable>RW2</replaceable> replication monitor</command>\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf -D \"cn=Directory Manager\" ldap://"
"<replaceable>RO3</replaceable> replication monitor</command>\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf -D \"cn=Directory Manager\" ldap://"
"<replaceable>RW1</replaceable> replication monitor</command>\n"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:554
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <command>dsctl</command> command has a <option>healthcheck</option> "
"option. The following example runs a replication healthcheck on the local "
"&ds389a; instance:"
msgstr ""
"また、 <command>dsctl</command> コマンドには <option>healthcheck</option> と"
"いうオプションもあります。下記ではローカルの &ds389a; インスタンスに対して、"
"レプリケーションの状態確認を行っています:"

#. Tag: screen
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:558
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsctl <replaceable>INSTANCE_NAME</replaceable> "
"healthcheck --check replication</command>\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsctl <replaceable>インスタンス名</replaceable> "
"healthcheck --check replication</command>\n"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:561
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <option>-v</option> option for verbosity, to see what the "
"healthcheck examines:"
msgstr ""
"<option>-v</option> オプションを追加すると、 healthcheck で行っていることの詳"
"細を表示することができます:"

#. Tag: screen
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:564
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsctl -v <replaceable>INSTANCE_NAME</replaceable> "
"healthcheck --check replication</command>\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsctl -v <replaceable>インスタンス名</replaceable> "
"healthcheck --check replication</command>\n"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:568
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Run <command>dsctl <replaceable>INSTANCE_NAME</replaceable> healthcheck</"
"command> with no options for a general health check."
msgstr ""
"オプション無しで <command>dsctl <replaceable>インスタンス名</replaceable> "
"healthcheck</command> を実行すると、一般的な状態確認のみを行います。"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:572
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Run the following command to see a list of the checks that healthcheck "
"performs:"
msgstr ""
"下記のようなコマンドを実行することで、 healthcheck を実行した際に行われる処理"
"の内容を調べることもできます:"

#. Tag: screen
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:576
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsctl <replaceable>INSTANCE_NAME</replaceable> "
"healthcheck --list-checks</command>\n"
"config:hr_timestamp\n"
"config:passwordscheme\n"
"backends:userroot:cl_trimming\n"
"backends:userroot:mappingtree\n"
"backends:userroot:search\n"
"backends:userroot:virt_attrs\n"
"encryption:check_tls_version\n"
"fschecks:file_perms\n"
"[...]\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsctl <replaceable>インスタンス名</replaceable> "
"healthcheck --list-checks</command>\n"
"config:hr_timestamp\n"
"config:passwordscheme\n"
"backends:userroot:cl_trimming\n"
"backends:userroot:mappingtree\n"
"backends:userroot:search\n"
"backends:userroot:virt_attrs\n"
"encryption:check_tls_version\n"
"fschecks:file_perms\n"
"[...]\n"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:588
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can run one or more of the individual checks:"
msgstr "個別のチェックのみを実行したい場合は、下記のように入力して実行します:"

#. Tag: screen
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:591
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsctl <replaceable>INSTANCE_NAME</replaceable> "
"healthcheck</command> \\\n"
"<command>--check monitor-disk-space:disk_space tls:certificate_expiration</"
"command>\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsctl <replaceable>インスタンス名</replaceable> "
"healthcheck</command> \\\n"
"<command>--check monitor-disk-space:disk_space tls:certificate_expiration</"
"command>\n"

#. Tag: title
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:598
#, no-c-format
msgid "Making backups"
msgstr "バックアップの作成"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:599
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When replication is enabled, you need to adjust your &ds389; backup strategy "
"(see <xref linkend=\"sec-security-ldap-backup\"/> to learn about making "
"backups). If you are using <command>db2ldif</command> , you must add the "
"<option>--replication</option> flag to ensure that replication metadata is "
"backed up. You should backup all servers in the topology. When restoring "
"from backup, start by restoring a single node of the topology, then "
"reinitialize all other nodes as new instances."
msgstr ""
"レプリケーションを有効化した場合は、 &ds389; のバックアップについてもいくつか"
"の調整を行う必要があります (一般的なバックアップ方法については <xref "
"linkend=\"sec-security-ldap-backup\"/> をお読みください) 。具体的には、バック"
"アップ時に <command>db2ldif</command> コマンドを実行している場合、 <option>--"
"replication</option> フラグを指定して、レプリケーションのメタデータを最初に"
"バックアップするようにしてください。また、バックアップは構成内の全てのサーバ"
"に対して行うものとし、バックアップからの復元に際しては、構成内の 1 ノードでの"
"み実施して、残りのノードは再初期化を行ってデータを複製してください。"

#. Tag: title
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:613
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pausing and resuming replication"
msgstr "レプリケーションの一時停止と再開"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:614
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can pause replication during maintenance windows, or anytime you need to "
"stop it. A node of the topology can only be offline for a maximum of days up "
"to the limit of the changelog (see <xref linkend=\"sec-security-ldap-"
"replication-changelog\"/> )."
msgstr ""
"メンテナンスやその他の運用上の理由で、レプリケーションを一時的に停止すること"
"ができます。なお、一時停止は変更履歴の保持日数で示された期間 (詳しくは <xref "
"linkend=\"sec-security-ldap-replication-changelog\"/> をお読みください) まで"
"続けることができます。"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:620
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <command>repl-agmt</command> command to pause replication. The "
"following example is on RW2:"
msgstr ""
"レプリケーションを一時停止するには、 <command>repl-agmt</command> コマンドを"
"使用します。 RW2 で一時停止する場合は、下記のように入力して実行します:"

#. Tag: screen
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:624
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>INSTANCE_NAME</replaceable> repl-"
"agmt disable</command> \\\n"
"<command>--suffix <replaceable>dc=EXAMPLE,dc=COM</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>RW2_to_RW1</replaceable></command>\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>インスタンス名</replaceable> repl-"
"agmt disable</command> \\\n"
"<command>--suffix <replaceable>dc=EXAMPLE,dc=COM</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>RW2_to_RW1</replaceable></command>\n"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:628
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following example re-enables replication:"
msgstr "再開する場合は、下記のように入力して実行します:"

#. Tag: screen
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:631
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>INSTANCE_NAME</replaceable> repl-"
"agmt enable</command> \\\n"
"<command>--suffix <replaceable>dc=EXAMPLE,dc=COM</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>RW2_to_RW1</replaceable></command>\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>インスタンス名</replaceable> repl-"
"agmt enable</command> \\\n"
"<command>--suffix <replaceable>dc=EXAMPLE,dc=COM</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>RW2_to_RW1</replaceable></command>\n"

#. Tag: title
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:638
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changelog max-age"
msgstr "Changelog max-age"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:639
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A replica can be offline for up to the length of time defined by the "
"changelog <option>max-age</option> option. <option>max-age</option> defines "
"the maximum age of any entry in the changelog. Any items older than the "
"<option>max-age</option> value are automatically removed."
msgstr ""
"レプリカを何らかの理由でしばらくオフラインにする場合には、最大で changelog "
"<option>max-age</option> で指定した時間までが許容されます。 <option>max-age</"
"option> オプションは過去の変更履歴を持つ長さを時間で指定するための値で、ここ"
"で指定したよりも過去の履歴は自動的に削除されます。"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:645
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After the replica comes back online, it synchronizes with the other "
"replicas. If it is offline for longer than the <option>max-age</option> "
"value, the replica needs to be re-initialized and refuses to accept or "
"provide changes to other nodes, as they may be inconsistent. The following "
"example sets the <option>max-age</option> to seven days:"
msgstr ""
"しばらくオフラインになっていたレプリカが復帰すると、通常のレプリケーションと"
"同様に、他のレプリカとの間で同期が行われます。 <option>max-age</option> で指"
"定したよりも長い時間オフラインであった場合は、一貫性を失うことから、他のノー"
"ドからの変更を拒否したり、他のノードへの変更送信を拒否したりするようになりま"
"す。下記の例では、 <option>max-age</option> を 7 日間に設定しています:"

#. Tag: screen
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:652
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>INSTANCE_NAME</replaceable></"
"command> \\\n"
"<command>replication set-changelog --max-age 7d</command> \\\n"
"<command>--suffix <replaceable>dc=EXAMPLE,dc=COM</replaceable></command>\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>インスタンス名</replaceable></"
"command> \\\n"
"<command>replication set-changelog --max-age 7d</command> \\\n"
"<command>--suffix <replaceable>dc=EXAMPLE,dc=COM</replaceable></command>\n"

#. Tag: title
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:660
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removing a replica"
msgstr "レプリカの削除"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:661
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove a replica, first fence the node to prevent any incoming changes or "
"reads. Then, find all servers that have incoming replication agreements with "
"the node you are removing, and remove them. The following example removes "
"RW2. Start by disabling the outbound replication agreement on RW1:"
msgstr ""
"レプリカを削除するには、まず他のノードに対して変更点の送信を停止する必要があ"
"ります。あとは削除するノードで受け付けていたレプリケーション合意を削除しま"
"す。下記の例では、 RW2 を削除する場合の例を示しています。まずは RW1 での発信"
"側レプリケーション合意を削除します:"

#. Tag: screen
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:667
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>INSTANCE_NAME</replaceable> repl-"
"agmt delete</command> \\\n"
"<command>--suffix <replaceable>dc=EXAMPLE,dc=COM</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>RW1_to_RW2</replaceable></command>\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>インスタンス名</replaceable> repl-"
"agmt delete</command> \\\n"
"<command>--suffix <replaceable>dc=EXAMPLE,dc=COM</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>RW1_to_RW2</replaceable></command>\n"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:671
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the replica you are removing, which in the following example is RW2, "
"remove all outbound agreements:"
msgstr ""
"あとは削除対象のレプリカ (この例では RW2) で、全ての送信側レプリケーション合"
"意を削除します:"

#. Tag: screen
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:674
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<?dbfo keep-together=\"always\"?>\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>INSTANCE_NAME</replaceable> repl-"
"agmt delete</command> \\\n"
"<command>--suffix <replaceable>dc=EXAMPLE,dc=COM</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>RW2_to_RW1</replaceable></command>\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>INSTANCE_NAME</replaceable> repl-"
"agmt delete</command> \\\n"
"<command>--suffix <replaceable>dc=EXAMPLE,dc=COM</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>RW2_to_RO3</replaceable></command>\n"
msgstr ""
"<?dbfo keep-together=\"always\"?>\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>インスタンス名</replaceable> repl-"
"agmt delete</command> \\\n"
"<command>--suffix <replaceable>dc=EXAMPLE,dc=COM</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>RW2_to_RW1</replaceable></command>\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>インスタンス名</replaceable> repl-"
"agmt delete</command> \\\n"
"<command>--suffix <replaceable>dc=EXAMPLE,dc=COM</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>RW2_to_RO3</replaceable></command>\n"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:680
#, no-c-format
msgid "Stop the instance on RW2:"
msgstr "あとは RW2 インスタンスを停止します:"

#. Tag: screen
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:683
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>systemctl stop dirsrv@<replaceable>INSTANCE_NAME</"
"replaceable>.service</command>\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>systemctl stop dirsrv@<replaceable>INSTANCE_NAME</"
"replaceable>.service</command>\n"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:686
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Then run the <command>cleanallruv</command> command to remove the replica ID "
"from the topology. The following example is run on RW1:"
msgstr ""
"最後に構成内に書かれているレプリカ ID を削除するため、 <command>cleanallruv</"
"command> コマンドを実行します。下記は RW1 で実行した場合の例です:"

#. Tag: screen
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:690
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>INSTANCE_NAME</replaceable> repl-"
"tasks cleanallruv</command> \\\n"
"<command>--suffix <replaceable>dc=EXAMPLE,dc=COM</replaceable> --replica-id "
"<replaceable>2</replaceable></command>\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>INSTANCE_NAME</replaceable> repl-"
"tasks list-cleanruv-tasks</command>\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>インスタンス名</replaceable> repl-"
"tasks cleanallruv</command> \\\n"
"<command>--suffix <replaceable>dc=EXAMPLE,dc=COM</replaceable> --replica-id "
"<replaceable>2</replaceable></command>\n"
"&prompt.sudo;<command>dsconf <replaceable>インスタンス名</replaceable> repl-"
"tasks list-cleanruv-tasks</command>\n"

#. Tag: title
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:698
#, no-c-format
msgid "Limitations on replication of &ds389;"
msgstr "&ds389; でのレプリケーションの制限"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:699
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The use of &ds389; is supported within the following replication limits:"
msgstr ""
"&ds389; でレプリケーションを使用する場合、下記のサポート制限があります:"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:704
#, no-c-format
msgid "A maximum of 8 read-write nodes"
msgstr "読み書き可能なノードは最大 8 個まで"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:709
#, no-c-format
msgid "A maximum of 20 replication hubs"
msgstr "レプリケーションハブは最大 20 個まで"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:714
#, no-c-format
msgid "A maximum of 100 read-only servers"
msgstr "読み込み専用のサーバは最大 100 個まで"

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap_replication.xml:719
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A maximum of 1 Winsync Active Directory consumer as a read-write node member"
msgstr ""
"読み書き可能なメンバーとしての Winsync Active Directory コンシューマは最大 1 "
"個まで"
